      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once the onion and mushrooms have caramelised, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>chopped thyme</strong> to the pan</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 1 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
