      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add<strong> </strong>the<strong> drained linguine </strong>and <strong>pulled chicken </strong>to the pan with the<strong> chicken stock</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until slightly thickened</p><p>Once thickened, remove the pan from the heat and add your<strong> crème fraîche</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>chicken breast &</strong> <strong>mushroom stroganoff</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the<strong> </strong>reserved starchy pasta water if the sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
